{"tid":1464100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"父子騎驢 倒為驢騎","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:25:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:59:21.000Z","uid":71279,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"457e8a30b7cbf6055a9ecd483b156abca1545628","tid":1464100,"uid":71279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:25:08.000Z","msg":"故事描述一對父子牽著一匹驢子準備進城求售一開始，路人指指點點說道：「怎麼有頭驢也不知道騎？」<br />\n<br />\n於是爸爸牽驢，兒子騎驢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n路人看到後，又皺起眉頭說：「這個兒子怎麼這麼不孝順？」父子倆趕快交換位置，爸爸騎驢，兒子牽驢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後路人看到又說：「這個爸爸怎麼這麼不愛護小朋友？」於是父子一起騎上驢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n路人一看，大驚失色：「這兩人怎麼這樣虐待動物？」最後父子兩人無計可施，只好合力把驢子扛進城門。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n故事的結局是，還沒走到市集，父子倆已經累得半死，驢子也因為掙脫掉入河中溺斃。<br />\n<br />\n其實同出面班民意撚一樣，成日話爭取更大民意，但根本冇可能得到所有人認同<br />\n最後為左民意搞到乜成果都冇<br />\n好似機場單嘢咁，為左爭取遊客支持，最後令到機場如常運作<br />\n咁你個不合作運動仲有乜意義<br />\n爭取民意嘅前提係要以目標同成果行先<br />\n宜家就調番轉，本末倒置<br />\n最後一句，please all and you will please none"},{"pid":"d0ba8bfdeefce18b15e4f1de5e6605b3a20b434d","tid":1464100,"uid":71279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:28:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"098ccbfc6ca3e4f8982ed00c86b4a92b07c21026","tid":1464100,"uid":71279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:28:36.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"0a8514a753228ed8a380c427cde5c62379ce1bce","tid":1464100,"uid":71279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:32:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fd9330354dae4ad40dc9065e609ee0e5e3c6ad84","tid":1464100,"uid":71279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:32:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ac3e037e5bf606fc850d30c48073655f9decd0ec","tid":1464100,"uid":71279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:32:35.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"23b1ca63b78d3dbb843df9394ee56f89a287e824","tid":1464100,"uid":2142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:33:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37bec5d8e42c70b224f9db860beaa9389a0c1f36","tid":1464100,"uid":71279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:33:39.000Z","msg":"比更多人睇"},{"pid":"68fd943b3f20bfc88148fd8f3524c42788f43430","tid":1464100,"uid":105878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:35:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c88d7fe1e1e882e202bf2f07885dc681f32d314","tid":1464100,"uid":71279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:38:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bcacb7dc90b1973aade721fc34f8af32bde19326","tid":1464100,"uid":68471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:39:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter/閘口出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了，無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},{"pid":"e2350c36f01f5234c4cc0bbb159770eef1c6ab73","tid":1464100,"uid":71279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:45:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"80b1c50db309f50b7361ff7e9f8494055cace69c","tid":1464100,"uid":71279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:45:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"534f83d9f2635ecee1e49a419a4203afbd56a9d8","tid":1464100,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:00:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9eb505887e410f9f2b5bc9a879fe5945fc8895d2","tid":1464100,"uid":71279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:55:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"935265db7615bfbaf4b698695b1353bcb2b93591","tid":1464100,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:59:21.000Z","msg":"今日連登既總結<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一百個人一百把聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你想滿足邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}